## 动作命令本地化

## upgradeaction 命令本地化
upgradeaction-command-help = 用法：upgradeaction <实体Uid> [等级]
upgradeaction-command-need-one-argument = upgradeaction 至少需要一个参数，即动作实体 uid。第二个可选参数为指定等级。
upgradeaction-command-max-two-arguments = upgradeaction 最多接受两个参数：动作实体 uid 和（可选的）目标等级。
upgradeaction-command-second-argument-not-number = upgradeaction 的第二个参数只能是数字。
upgradeaction-command-less-than-required-level = upgradeaction 不接受 0 或更低的等级。
upgradeaction-command-incorrect-entityuid-format = upgradeaction 必须使用有效的实体 uid 格式。
upgradeaction-command-entity-does-not-exist = 该实体不存在，upgradeaction 需要一个有效实体。
upgradeaction-command-entity-is-not-action = 该实体没有动作升级组件，因此无法升级此动作。
upgradeaction-command-cannot-level-up = 该动作无法升级。
upgradeaction-command-description = 将动作升级一级，或升级至指定等级（如适用）。
